{"tid":475247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何志平被捕】撐《國歌法》在港立法 網民：為國捐軀，人民不會忘記！","createTime":"2017-11-21T03:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T14:52:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"75b0ceb393893891bdeb96ab54d5cb61dce23362","tid":475247,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511228120_7d00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511228120_7d00.jpg&h=5376a9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511227822_3201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511227822_3201.jpg&h=03cbe9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民政事務局前局長何志平與塞內加爾前外長，涉嫌代表一間中國能源公司賄賂非洲官員，二人在美國時間18日在紐約被捕。何志平擔任「中華能源基金委員會」主席，熱心投入中國外交工作，更開設微博帳戶，以「何之評論」發表評論文章，最後一篇的文章於5月2日貼在微博，題為「中美締默契談判解朝鮮關係？」<br />\n<br />\n最近一次見報為9月接受內地新華社專訪，他支持《國歌法》在港立法，認為很多國家都有國歌法，其意義不僅在於規範國歌的唱法和唱國歌時應有的禮儀，更是讓國民尤其是下一代認識和尊重這一國家的象徵。他說：「國歌是一個國家的象徵。香港回歸祖國了，怎麼能不播我們自己的國歌？」<br />\n<br />\n在5月，他則力撐「一帶一路」是兩岸融合發展的途徑，強調「台灣一定要加入『一帶一路』，台灣經濟的唯一的出路就是登上『一帶一路』的經濟快車。」他指出，兩岸已經隔絕近70年，「久分必合」，「一帶一路」是個很好的機會。「今天絲綢古路的新生將為中華民族偉大復興提供新的動力，成為中華民族重新屹立於世界民族之林前列的標誌。而中華民族偉大復興中國夢的實現，必然包括台灣同胞在內。」<br />\n<br />\n網民對於何志平被捕，揶揄他「以為自己有外交豁免權？」「不過強國越境執法才是真正強國。聯合國是藏污納垢的垃圾地方。往往給美帝莫名的巨大權力。」「為國捐軀！」「辛苦你了，人民不會忘記」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171121/57484247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484247&d=YHB6s8ga2I4eb32L6MIQwP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7af6f0a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484247&h=0a3a3079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171121/57484247</a>"},{"pid":"ef964e92d260fed8e3fca5c836f7de300002584a","tid":475247,"uid":50740,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"肚滿腸肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62bf7666365d7a1d874395992cd8613b3d363e8","tid":475247,"uid":8048,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"一賄一賂 好風光"},{"pid":"6c544fe682052675b40fde514cc1aad9404c4be8","tid":475247,"uid":39200,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:26:10.000Z","msg":"等睇華春瑩出黎話隻肥佬唔係中國公民，事件同中國無關"},{"pid":"281679cd48247482e5563da55a2b90aaa4260d44","tid":475247,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇華春瑩出黎話隻肥佬唔係中國公民，事件同中國無關</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c89d7ab71f700247317303f355b555067154848","tid":475247,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"689出來講兩句"},{"pid":"1d836bd584c1a2cf753644e88f5ff6c08ff84d3c","tid":475247,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:33:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱係新聞都聽到。"},{"pid":"8c9ab42b19a1457285d78856c401999ac5cf59f0","tid":475247,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"97之後香港高官終於可以衝出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea51ce3e4cb9f5c3de16b5844243b6fe585a8bd2","tid":475247,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ce05886d1e0a84921bd144c3cc44d8d2829a3f","tid":475247,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl